24:53.575 --> 24:55.577
[indistinct chatter]

24:57.704 --> 24:59.789
-[keys clinking]
-[sighs]

25:01.082 --> 25:03.335
If only you could
shine a light on the darkness,

25:03.418 --> 25:06.796
