26:14.489 --> 26:17.575
Okay. I just wanted to hear your voice.

26:19.077 --> 26:20.578
Give him a kiss from Dad.

26:23.248 --> 26:24.416
Love you too.

26:34.301 --> 26:35.343
[Tench] I'm sorry, Ed,

26:35.427 --> 26:38.555
do you mean that violence in the movies
drove you to kill those women?

26:38.638 --> 26:39.597
