where there aren't people watching,

27:42.535 --> 27:43.870
but I say, "No, I can't."

27:43.953 --> 27:46.122
So you picked up women
but didn't kill them?

27:46.206 --> 27:49.042
But then, a gun is in the car,

27:49.125 --> 27:50.877
and this craving,

27:50.960 --> 27:54.506
this awful raging, eating feeling
is inside me.

27:55.757 --> 27:57.467
I would've loved to have just raped them,

27:58.051 --> 28:00.553
but not having any experience at all,

28:01.054 --> 28:04.974
I could feel it consuming my insides,
this fantastic passion.

28:05.058 --> 28:06.935
Fantastic passion?

28:07.018 --> 28:10.271
-It's a good phrase, no?
-Then what happens?

28:10.355 --> 28:12.315
You know, I'm thinking of writing
my own book.

28:12.399 --> 28:15.360
I've been trying to get a typewriter.
Maybe help me with that?

28:15.443 --> 28:17.404
I'm sure we could pull some strings.

28:17.695 --> 28:19.280
Then it builds, the feeling?

28:19.364 --> 28:20.949
At some point, you begin to...

28:21.408 --> 28:23.243
-enjoy the thrill.
-[Ed] Look...

28:24.077 --> 28:26.204
when you slit a person's throat,

28:26.287 --> 28:28.331
you need to cut it from ear to ear

28:28.415 --> 28:31.376
in order to sever the windpipe
and the jugular

28:31.459 --> 28:33.711
so that they bleed and suffocate
at the same time.

28:33.795 --> 28:35.880
Otherwise, they'll just be
in a great deal of pain.

28:37.298 --> 28:39.718
That's how I learnt the term "ear to ear,"

28:39.801 --> 28:41.094
literally, what that meant.

28:41.177 --> 28:43.513
People think it's just an expression.

28:43.596 --> 28:45.473
It's not, it's an instruction.

28:45.557 --> 28:48.309
You don't want to. You have to.

28:48.393 --> 28:49.769
So there's no pleasure, Ed?

28:49.853 --> 28:51.104
[Ed] Sure there is.

28:51.187 --> 28:53.982
I just wanted the exaltation
over the party.

28:54.607 --> 28:56.443
In other words, winning over death.

28:57.026 --> 28:59.821
They were dead and I was alive.
That was the pleasure.

28:59.904 --> 29:02.615
I was the hunter, they were my victims.

29:02.699 --> 29:04.743
So how did you feel
after your first kills?

29:07.620 --> 29:09.831
[clears throat, sighs]

29:11.416 --> 29:13.501
I liked Mary the best.

29:13.585 --> 29:15.503
