by her personality and her looks,

29:29.142 --> 29:31.686
and there was just almost
a reverence there.

29:31.770 --> 29:33.855
-Reverence?
-Sure.

29:34.355 --> 29:36.441
Sometimes, afterward,
I visited there to be near her

29:36.524 --> 29:38.359
because I loved her and wanted her.

29:39.027 --> 29:40.278
At the murder site?

29:40.361 --> 29:42.363
I've never been much to look at myself,

29:42.447 --> 29:44.866
but I've always gone after
the pretty girls.

29:44.949 --> 29:46.034
I bet you're the same.

29:47.619 --> 29:48.620
Sure.

29:49.829 --> 29:51.539
You probably can't imagine this,

29:51.623 --> 29:54.542
but since I was locked up
from age 15 to 21

29:54.626 --> 29:56.711
for the murder of my grandparents,

29:56.795 --> 30:00.256
I was very much out of touch
with women my own age.

30:00.799 --> 30:04.344
When I got back on the street,
it was like being on a strange planet.

30:04.928 --> 30:07.555
I had been living with people
older than I was for so long,

30:07.639 --> 30:09.140
I was like an old fogy.

30:09.224 --> 30:10.809
