31:23.965 --> 31:26.009
You know,
that night I walked up to her bed.

31:26.092 --> 31:30.471
She's laying there reading a paperback,
as many thousands of nights before.

31:31.598 --> 31:36.811
She says, "Oh, I suppose you're gonna
want to wait up all night and talk now."

31:38.229 --> 31:39.564
Can you believe that?

31:40.231 --> 31:42.317
"Wait up all night talking."

31:43.526 --> 31:44.569
Shit.

31:47.405 --> 31:49.240
And I knew I was gonna kill her...

31:50.158 --> 31:51.075
you know?

31:52.327 --> 31:54.662
