for the first time.

31:56.414 --> 31:58.458
Because I'm not a lizard,

31:58.541 --> 32:01.920
I'm not from under a rock,
I came out of her vagina.

32:02.587 --> 32:03.796
I came out of my mother.

32:05.006 --> 32:08.426
Is it true that you put part of her
into the garbage disposal?

32:10.595 --> 32:12.013
Her vocal cords.

32:12.680 --> 32:13.848
Why?

32:13.932 --> 32:15.600
Because I couldn't shut her up.

32:16.100 --> 32:20.188
She wanted to destroy me
with words, literally.

32:20.271 --> 32:21.940
So I shut her up for good.

32:23.274 --> 32:26.319
And now, everyone knows it was
because of what she did to me,

32:26.402 --> 32:28.947
because of the way she treated her son.

32:33.534 --> 32:36.788
