32:38.581 --> 32:39.624
Pizza!

32:40.541 --> 32:41.918
You guys.

32:44.587 --> 32:47.215
Okay. So you get out of the car...

32:47.507 --> 32:50.718
-I just walk into the apartment building.
-Anyone around?

32:50.802 --> 32:51.844
So, I'm home,

32:51.928 --> 32:54.013
