33:07.527 --> 33:10.238
-They walk right past me.
-Your two worlds are colliding...

33:10.321 --> 33:12.865
My murderous fantasy life and this.

33:12.949 --> 33:16.077
Pretty girl. Pretty name.
Kim or something.

33:16.494 --> 33:18.246
